---
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<Section>
  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-12">
    Phineas is a Senior Software Engineer with 15+ years of experience in web development, specializing in
    building frontend solutions for web, mobile and TV platforms, who thrives in a team of
    high achievers who value continuous learning and mutual growth.	
  </p>		

  <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12 sm:px-12">
    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <div class="flex-none flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Full-Stack Expertise</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Deep experience across the entire web development stack, with particular strength in frontend architecture and modern frameworks.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <div class="flex-none flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.042 21.672L13.684 16.6m0 0l-2.51 2.225.569-9.47 5.227 7.917-3.286-.672zM12 2.25V4.5m5.834.166l-1.591 1.591M20.25 10.5H18M7.757 14.743l-1.59 1.59M6 10.5H3.75m4.007-4.243l-1.59-1.59" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Product-Focused Engineer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Proven track record of delivering complex web applications with a focus on user experience and business impact.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex gap-4">
      <div class="flex-none flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
