      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-1">Team Leadership</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Experienced in mentoring engineers, driving technical decisions, and fostering a culture of engineering excellence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
